{"tid":1357143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係想讚何妖 但佢係幾有EQ","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:10:50.000Z","uid":86077,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7b3058eb626ce4830972e79a6b8b4527e757ff00","tid":1357143,"uid":86077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"睇到想打爆個mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係！<br />\n香港人你地好忙架 唔好嘥時間理條仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完條撚樣係時候要睇番<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求</span></span>啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一 徹底撤回修例<br />\n二 收回暴動定義<br />\n三 撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四 徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五 以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n721上環開左36槍，有義士中槍<br />\n同時元朗白衣暴徒無差別襲擊普通市民<br />\n黑警同佢地搭晒膊頭懶理市民生命安全<br />\n亦有手足以死相諫<br />\n然而林鄭仲係覺得個國徽整污糟左少少比以上既所有野重要<br />\n槍頭要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></span>呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好唔記得<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">社會評分同監控燈柱</span></span>仲繼續起緊<br />\n係咪要等全香港啲燈柱起好晒先知驚<br />\n到時想反都反唔到啦<br />\nThis is <span style=\"color: red;\">HONG KONG</span> not china"},{"pid":"3d362ee2e89e8364da28d22331ea8e8d90987e29","tid":1357143,"uid":86077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"842ce0c382557b2187f19912ec64b1d50c36264e","tid":1357143,"uid":86077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:09:38.